## Checksum

08|09|00|09|04|08 = 38 => Even
90|00|80|10|70|90 = 34 => Odd

38 * 3 = 114 => Even * 3
114 + 34 = 148 => (Even * 3) + Odd
148 % 10 = 8
10 - 8 = 2

## Theory

According to [this](https://www.barcoding.com/blog/barcode-prefixes-and-product-country-of-origin/) article,
980 is for *refund receipts*
